Name: Palante
Review Text: Very cozy place in a less hectic part of Zuidas with chilling music and food of outstanding quality! Many offers of alternative food and craft beers. Food prices on Amsterdam level, alcoholic beverages comparatively cheap.

Name: Palante
Review Text: A pleasant surprise, so close to the business district. The available dishes are quite varied, and vegetarian friendly. The ambiance is really pleasant.

Name: Palante
Review Text: Beautiful and relaxed with great atmosphere. I had the beetroot salad, the Bali-coconut-beans, the artichoke-potatoes and the Harissa-chicken. Everything was really good.

Name: Palante
Review Text: It's a super cozy place with amazing slow cooked food and good atmosphere, full of books. I loved having lunch and reading there :)

Name: Palante
Review Text: Lovely vegetarian & vegan food. Also for meat lovers e.g. stew. Good ambiance and pleasant terrace.

Name: Palante
Review Text: Cosy atmosphere with a few local craft beers

Name: Palante
Review Text: Great service, lovely atmosphere, great for any occasion.

Name: Palante
Review Text: Very nice ambience with excellent food and remarkable service.

Name: Palante
Review Text:
Delicious food, Great location
highly recommended!!

Name: Palante
Review Text: Nice food and drinks. Workers are friendly.
